block.data: This session will provide an overview of the EU policy activities regarding RFID and Privacy in 2007 and give an outlook to activities planned for 2008. EDRi's positions on RFID and Privacy will be presented and, when published by the Commission before the event, the contents of the Recommendation to the member states will be presented and discussed in detail.
